WEBVTT

00:01:28.758 --> 00:01:30.593
Shunday jarayon...

00:01:31.500 --> 00:01:34.076
Keyin esa ikki oy bir oyga aylandi,

00:01:34.100 --> 00:01:35.725
keyin ikki haftaga.

00:01:35.749 --> 00:01:37.058
Bir kuni uyg'onsam,

00:01:37.724 --> 00:01:40.343
topshirish kunigacha uch kun qolgan.

00:01:41.502 --> 00:01:43.433
Menda birorta so'z ham yozilmagan.

00:01:43.457 --> 00:01:45.516
Shuning uchun men yagona yo'lni tanladim:

00:01:45.540 --> 00:01:48.147
90 ta betni 72 soatda yozdim.

00:01:48.171 --> 00:01:50.447
Bittamas, ikkita to'liq tunni 
uyqusiz o'tkazib.

00:01:50.471 --> 00:01:53.040
Inson uchun ikkita ketma-ket uyqusiz tun 
juda zarar.

00:01:54.373 --> 00:01:56.276
Butun kampus bo'ylab yugurib bordim,

00:01:56.290 --> 00:01:58.026
sekinlashtirilgan kadrdagidek.

00:01:58.050 --> 00:01:59.956
Oxirgi soniyada topshirishga ulgurdim.

00:01:59.980 --> 00:02:02.004
Endi hammasini qutuldim deb o'ylagan edim.